               <p>A pawnbroker brought me a silver-spoon with my mark upon it, I do not know that I have lost one; I <rs id="t17890708-52-viclabel257" type="occupation">keep <placeName id="t17890708-52-crimeloc258">Hudson's Coffee-house, Covent-Garden</placeName>
